00:04:04.977 --> 00:04:06.759
and in this type of racing

00:04:06.759 --> 00:04:08.727
especially when we were coming 
into a 24-hour race,

00:04:08.753 --> 00:04:10.799
we have to be careful and

00:04:10.799 --> 00:04:14.609
